Know Your Role: Support
data.description: New to Overwatch League? Let some of our pro players introduce you to some of the roles you could be playing with your team in this three-part explainer series. Not only do you need the heavy hitters from Tank and DPS, you need heavy lifters like Support. neptuNo (Philadelphia Fusion), Bdosin (London Spitfire), ArK (New York Excelsior), and BigGoose (Los Angeles Gladiators) are some of the best Support players in the Overwatch League. They break down how Support can hold a team together, execute certain plays, and even boost your team in the tightest situations in this installment of Know Your Role.

Know Your Role: DPS
data.description: New to Overwatch League? Let some of our pro players introduce you to some of the roles you could be playing with your team in this three-part explainer series. Playing DPS is more than just who can shoot or slash the fastest. Three of the top damage dealers in Overwatch League Saebyeolbe (New York Excelsior), Surefour (Los Angeles Gladiators), Carpe (Philadelphia Fusion), and SoOn (Los Angeles Valiant) show you that it’s all about placement, timing, and precision in this installment of Know Your Role.

data.title: Know Your Role: Tank
data.description: New to Overwatch League? Let some of our pro players introduce you to some of the roles you could be playing with your team in this three-part explainer series. Want to know what it takes to play Tank in Overwatch? Four of our top Overwatch League pro’s, Fissure (LA Gladiators), Note (Boston Uprising), Gesture (London Spitfire) and Space (LA Valiant) tell you everything you need to know to push your team to victory.
